{"tid":1738502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［11.20］各位勇武手足入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-11-19T09:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T10:30:16.000Z","uid":222623,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"261de2efef4dd0bd9df3dac605d6078fa5a4411c","tid":1738502,"uid":222623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:16:43.000Z","msg":"根據過往經驗 三罷行動雖然好成功<br />\n但係通常5:30開始搞都有個問題<br />\n就係教育局唔會係7點-8點停課！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁即是點？ 就算遲到學生一樣要行路返學<br />\n咁不如分兩段時間 夜深行動 5:30行動<br />\n其他手足犧牲自己 你唔係連瞓覺時間都唔捨得付出？<br />\n各位巴絲凌晨12開始行動 尤其係夜深無人時段<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住！係各區每個路口嘅燈都要打爆<br />\n做到真正嘅癱瘓交通<br />\n有車嘅巴絲就盡量行慢d 或者停車係路中心<br />\n無車嘅可以幫手掟垃圾落條鐵路到<br />\n冷氣軍師嘅可以幫手推行動post<br />\n千奇唔好單拖 搵手足一齊行動 齊上齊落</span></span>"},{"pid":"8310466e691bd136b1e812630be304b2a23a6d7e","tid":1738502,"uid":222623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:17:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"726786f1924522647dc58664784f52050837a1fc","tid":1738502,"uid":222623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:18:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8073dfa8e55f5ba2601c2a9d6b642810faf5c53d","tid":1738502,"uid":222623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:18:20.000Z","msg":"幫手置頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264e72071d18a513d43b95016132b9fcfc17a416","tid":1738502,"uid":340080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3dfjgWw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dfjgWw.jpg&h=bacac914&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"237c36de29c0dfb175448ca81a28ff4ea9fe0003","tid":1738502,"uid":222623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:20:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f4bdfa7a1303ed6552c8ed5eae71abd061d057c3","tid":1738502,"uid":222623,"like":0,"d